snippet.title: Aztech Forgotten Gods - Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The time is nigh. Tenochtitlan's fate is in your hands!
Be ready to face off against the fearsome deities of the past and fulfill your destiny when Aztech Forgotten Gods launches on March 10, 2022 for Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch and Windows PC via Steam and the Epic Games Store!

Aztech will support English, Spanish, French, Italian, German, and Russian languages.
